    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335640/extras/b4785d35dd0089815ce02a3a1286cef5.webp?t=1707748229\" width=489 height=30 /></span><br><br>Epic and emotional epic quest: Experience a story that explores themes of self-discovery and inner strength, wacky/humorous scenes with selectable choices and tributes to movies or other videogames.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335640/extras/d9df2cf29f1e691aa2ff47d2df670116.poster.avif?t=1707748229\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335640/extras/d9df2cf29f1e691aa2ff47d2df670116.webm?t=1707748229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335640/extras/d9df2cf29f1e691aa2ff47d2df670116.mp4?t=1707748229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play like it's 1994!: Enjoy a nostalgic experience with classic CRT-style graphics, a selectable filter that turns your monitor to a cathode ray tube TV, bringing the look and feel of Golden era of JRPGs and games of '80s-'90s.<br><br>Intense Battles: Battle against fearsome monsters and powerful enemies using a range of weapons and spells, with fast-paced, turn-based combat that will put your skills to the test.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335640/extras/907cd17fbb995020a0e5d4232b954c09.webp?t=1707748229\" width=569 height=30 /></span><br><br>Piano-Driven Soundtrack: Immerse yourself in the emotional journey with a beautiful and evocative soundtrack, featuring emotional piano melodies, composed by the developer, that perfectly complement the game's themes that will stay with you long after the credits roll.<br><br>Character Development: Customize and develop your characters over time, choosing from a range of equipments and abilities that will shape your journey and determine your ultimate fate.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335640/extras/23b0e701745bd9bcbee5f22498472c38.webp?t=1707748229\" width=556 height=30 /></span><br><br>Tons of content: With multiple endings, side quests with unique rewards, minigames, extra dungeons, challenges, optional characters and hidden secrets, you'll have plenty of reasons to revisit the world of &quot;Kay’s Destiny&quot; again and again.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335640/extras/cff148efb895c95744a2e5f02797c204.webp?t=1707748229\" width=374 height=30 /></span><br><br>Discover and dominate hidden powers that will help you in your way opening new paths or making you discover useful special items.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335640/extras/67c3a705a417046675d339393485d41b.webp?t=1707748229\" width=456 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335640/extras/f42c6b0d2f5fa5860297360d9aac9fbd.poster.avif?t=1707748229\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335640/extras/f42c6b0d2f5fa5860297360d9aac9fbd.webm?t=1707748229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335640/extras/f42c6b0d2f5fa5860297360d9aac9fbd.mp4?t=1707748229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Find and ride ships, steampunk machines, airships and so on!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335640/extras/9fc8c900865e05ad0cae498e57cd3547.webp?t=1707748229\" width=698 height=30 /></span><br><br>Completionists will be rewarded by something special that goes beyond the game itself!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335640/extras/23cfa3d6ab7eccaabbb7a812877bb45a.avif?t=1707748229\" width=370 height=125 /></span>",
